				For all you shamans wanting to get the helm....<BR>
1) I'm not sure where the glacier bear spawns, but that is not important. The important thing is that once it does spawn it moves.  (It roams around the whole cave)  And you ask, &quot;But how do I know where its at?&quot;  Simple...remember that spell called sense animals?  Use it.  If that bear is anywhere in that cave you will point straight towards it.  (This spell can be purchased at the gypsy camp in Oasis)  I bound myself in the cave and checked back every four hours or so.  Every four hours either the roaming skeleton spawns or the bear.  Good luck=)  
