			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				  To get to the cave where the glacier bear is, goto the frozen river next to megans tower.  If you go directly to the river from the tower you should see a hole in the ice.  U need enduring breath to get to the cave, its a while.  Jump in the hole and swim to the left, toward the mountains, eventually u will surface in a cave, then u can mix it up with the glacier bear.
				</font>
