				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Frankly, this is the best piece of the new shaman only armor. +5 wis is one wis point better than a Runed Circlet and looks better to boot. Don't know much about the glacier bear pelt other than it spawns in Everfrost in a cave that can be found by swimming under the ice. Anyone know how tough the bear is? Also the other piece needed for this is bone barbs from Barbed Bone Skeletons in Unrest. That's the easy part. The bear is the hard part and from what I've heard a most tedious camp.  Also, if anyone has any info on where the bear spawns in the cave it would be much appreciated. One last note, there is also a VERY aggro and VERY red conning spellcaster (At least to me, level 35) patrolling the cave. Took one look and gated out. Happy hunting all.
